The paper deals with a machine learning algorithm for regression problems, specifically the problem of learning heterogeneous regression ensembles. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of meta-features, which is related to data mining (cs.DM) and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper mentions the use of decision trees, which is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE).
